room_title: Escape room "House of El'Dred" by Race 2 Xcape in Springfield (MO)
room_address: 4560 S. Campbell, Ste L128 Springfield, MO 65810
room_description: Your long-lost friend suddenly turns up with tickets to the famous "House of El'Dred" and wants you and several friends to join him for a special dinner to celebrate. Your curiosity overcomes any hesitation you may feel, and you decide to attend. What surprises await you and the other attending guests?
